import React from 'react'
import Wrapper from './style'

const Teacher= () => {
  return (
    <Wrapper>
      <main>
        <form className='year'>
          <input type="button" value="I" />
          <input type="button" value="II" />
          <input type="button" value="III" />
          <input type="button" value="IV" />
        </form>
        <form className='searchfor'>
          <input type="text" placeholder='Search'/>
          <input type="button" value="Search" />
        </form>
        <form className='select'>
          <input type="button" value="CS-I-A" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-I-B" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-I-C" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-II-A" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-II-B" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-II-C" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-III-A" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-III-B" />
          <input type="button" value="CS-III-C" />
        </form>
    </main>
        
    </Wrapper>
    
  )
}

export default Teacher
